        {
            "title": "民主黨公佈來自司法部的愛潑斯坦相關照片 川普和柯林頓均在其列",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國眾議院民主黨發布了一批來自已故金融家傑弗裡·愛潑斯坦莊園的新照片，其中包括總統川普、前總統柯林頓、比爾·蓋茲和拉裡·薩默斯的身影。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些照片沒有日期，照片中的川普尚未成為美國總統。英國國王查爾斯三世的弟弟安德魯·蒙巴頓·溫莎也在照片中。所有人都否認有任何不當行為。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">眾議員Robert Garcia在星期五的電子郵件聲明中表示，這19張照片是司法部提供的9.5萬張照片的一部分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Garcia說，司法部提供的照片裡還有女性和愛潑斯坦財產，他們將繼續向公眾發布這些照片。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d1d0c02f-07f4-3b5a-b50d-e61fc07a9404-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump, Clinton Included in Democrats’ Release of Epstein Photos</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%BB%A8%E5%85%AC%E4%BD%88%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%84%9B%E6%BD%91%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%92%8C%E6%9F%AF%E6%9E%97%E9%A0%93%E5%9D%87%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%B6%E5%88%97-173353846.html",
